						<img src="/assets/University-of-Michigan.jpg" alt="University of Michigan Logo" width="50" height="50" class="logo" />
						<strong>University of Michigan</strong> - Python Programming, Jan 2020 - Dec 2023, <em>Grade: A+</em>.
					</p>
					<p>
